	<tr><td valign=top align=left colspan="2"><hr size="1"></td></tr>
	<tr><td valign=top align=left colspan="2" class="text">Personal Contact listing lists all the personal contacts.</td></tr>
	<tr><td valign=top align=left colspan="2" class="text"><IMG src="/help/images/clear.gif" height=5 width=1 border=0></td></tr>
	<tr><td valign=top align=left colspan="2" class="subheader">Adding A Contact</td></tr>
	<tr><td valign=top align=left colspan="2" class="text">Click on the <strong>New Contact</strong> button to create new contact. See Help on Adding A New Contact.</td></tr>
	<tr><td valign=top align=left colspan="2" class="text"><IMG src="/help/images/clear.gif" height=5 width=1 border=0></td></tr>
	<tr><td valign=top align=left colspan="2" class="subheader">Creating A Distribution List</td></tr>
	<tr><td valign=top align=left colspan="2" class="text">Click on the <strong>New Distribution List </strong> link to create new distribution list. See Help on Creating New Contact.</td></tr>
	<tr><td valign=top align=left colspan="2" class="text"><IMG src="/help/images/clear.gif" height=5 width=1 border=0></td></tr>
	<tr><td valign=top align=left colspan="2" class="subheader">Delete Contact</td></tr>
    <tr>
		<td valign=top align=left width=22 class="text">1.</td>
		<td valign=top align=left class="text">To delete a contact, put a tick in checkbox at contact you wish to remove.</td>
	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td valign=top align=left width=22 class="text">2.</td>
		<td valign=top align=left class="text">Click on the <strong>Delete</strong> button, a confirmation pop-up message will appear before the contact is deleted. Click on the <strong>OK</strong> button to delete or <strong>Cancel</strong> button to cancel.</td>
	</tr>
	<tr><td valign=top align=left colspan="2" class="text"><IMG src="/help/images/clear.gif" height=5 width=1 border=0></td></tr>
	<tr><td valign=top align=left colspan="2" class="subheader">Send Message</td></tr>
	<tr>
		<td valign=top align=left width=22 class="text">1.</td>
		<td valign=top align=left class="text">To send a message to a contact(s), put a tick in checkbox at selected contact.</td>
	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td valign=top align=left width=22 class="text">2.</td>
		<td valign=top align=left class="text">Click on the <strong>Send Message</strong> button, it will direct you to the <strong>Compose Message</strong> page with the selected contact(s) in the <strong>To</strong> field.</td>
	</tr>
	<tr><td valign=top align=left colspan="2" class="text"><IMG src="/help/images/clear.gif" height=5 width=1 border=0></td></tr>
	<tr><td valign=top align=left colspan="2" class="subheader">Move Contact</td></tr>
	<tr><td valign=top align=left colspan="2" class="text">A contact can be moved from one folder to another folder.</td></tr>
	<tr>
		<td valign=top align=left width=22 class="text">1.</td>
		<td valign=top align=left class="text">To move a contact, put a tick in checkbox at selected contact.</td>
	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td valign=top align=left width=22 class="text">2.</td>
		<td valign=top align=left class="text">Select which target folder to move from the <strong>Folders</strong> list.</td>
	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td valign=top align=left width=22 class="text">3.</td>
		<td valign=top align=left class="text">Click on the <strong>Move</strong> button to move, the contact will be moved to the targetted folder.</td>
	</tr>
</table>
